    [phosphor-pid-control] Remove blind exception handler
    Summary: We are noticing cases where we are experiencing fd exhaustion.
    This shows up as a caught exception here, and everything is retried.
    
    Removing this for testing, so that we can see which exceptions are
    normally raised and we can handle them appropriately
    
